{"error": null, "result": {"nr": 125, "upvote_ids": [], "change_log": [{"type": "create", "when": "2015-03-17T02:57:11Z", "uid": "hs2ssz7dkh76h6", "data": "i7cplscbcwe7g0", "anon": "no"}, {"uid": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "to": "i7cplsc6zxg7fz", "when": "2015-03-17T03:39:53Z", "anon": "no", "data": "i7cr4pbql0i5hx", "type": "i_answer"}, {"type": "i_answer_update", "when": "2015-03-17T03:40:45Z", "uid": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "data": "i7cr5tyzd5n1k2", "anon": "no"}, {"type": "followup", "to": "i7cplsc6zxg7fz", "when": "2015-03-17T05:13:24Z", "uid": "hs2ssz7dkh76h6", "anon": "no"}, {"type": "feedback", "to": "i7cplsc6zxg7fz", "when": "2015-03-17T16:15:56Z", "uid": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "anon": "no"}, {"type": "followup", "to": "i7cplsc6zxg7fz", "when": "2015-03-21T14:46:00Z", "uid": "i78odcf1aiM", "anon": "no"}, {"type": "feedback", "to": "i7cplsc6zxg7fz", "when": "2015-03-22T03:09:31Z", "uid": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "anon": "no"}], "q_edits": [], "i_edits": [], "unique_views": 80, "bookmarked": 4, "config": {}, "history": [{"subject": "SETGATE宏的第二个参数istrap的设置", "content": "<p>在给出的答案中&#xff0c;所有istrap全部设置为0. 而根据mmu.h中的定义&#xff0c;istrap用来区分异常和中断。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>我以为合适的实现方式应该如下所示&#xff1a;</p>\n<p></p>\n<pre>    int i;\n    for (i = 0; i &lt; 256; i &#43;&#43;) {\n        if (i == T_SYSCALL) {\n            SETGATE(idt[i], 1, GD_KTEXT, __vectors[i], DPL_USER)\n        }\n        else if (i &lt; IRQ_OFFSET) {\n            SETGATE(idt[i], 1, GD_KTEXT, __vectors[i], DPL_KERNEL)\n        }\n        else {\n            SETGATE(idt[i], 0, GD_KTEXT, __vectors[i], DPL_KERNEL)\n        }\n    }</pre>\n<p>即应该区分异常和中断对istrap参数进行不同的设置。</p>\n<p>而不是参考答案中的</p>\n<pre>    int i;\n    for (i = 0; i &lt; sizeof(idt) / sizeof(struct gatedesc); i &#43;&#43;) {\n        SETGATE(idt[i], 0, GD_KTEXT, __vectors[i], DPL_KERNEL);\n    }\n\t// set for switch from user to kernel\n    SETGATE(idt[T_SWITCH_TOK], 0, GD_KTEXT, __vectors[T_SWITCH_TOK], DPL_USER);</pre>\n<p></p>", "created": "2015-03-17T02:57:11Z", "uid": "hs2ssz7dkh76h6", "anon": "no"}], "data": {"embed_links": []}, "request_instructor_me": false, "folders": ["lab1"], "type": "question", "tag_good": [{"class_sections": ["课程设计_i5j09fnsl7k5x0"], "admin": true, "role": "instructor", "facebook_id": null, "us": false, "name": "Yu Chen", "id": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "photo": "1378950179_35.png"}, {"admin": false, "role": "student", "facebook_id": null, "us": false, "name": "郭子雷", "id": "i78odcf1aiM", "photo": null}], "no_answer": 0, "created": "2015-03-17T02:57:11Z", "t": 1433500102383, "id": "i7cplsc6zxg7fz", "status": "active", "tag_good_arr": ["hcrrjuyequh4bt", "i78odcf1aiM"], "default_anonymity": "no", "my_favorite": false, "bucket_order": 2, "is_bookmarked": false, "is_tag_good": false, "bucket_name": "Today", "no_answer_followup": 0, "children": [{"folders": [], "bucket_order": 2, "config": {}, "history": [{"subject": "", "content": "<p>很好&#xff01;我理解这样更加准确&#xff01;多谢&#xff01;</p>\n<p>我会尽快合并到labcodes_answer中</p>\n<p>另外&#xff0c;参考答案只是一个参考&#xff0c;并不是正确或唯一的解&#xff0c;请大家在实验时注意&#xff01;</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>我的问题&#xff1a;如果采用老的实现&#xff0c;请问会出现什么不是我们期望的现象&#xff1f;有一个例子吗&#xff1f;</p>", "created": "2015-03-17T03:40:45Z", "uid": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "anon": "no"}, {"subject": "", "content": "<p>很好&#xff01;我理解这样更加准确&#xff01;多谢&#xff01;</p>\n<p>我会尽快合并到labcodes_answer中</p>\n<p>另外&#xff0c;参考答案只是一个参考&#xff0c;并不是正确或唯一的解&#xff0c;请大家在实验时注意&#xff01;</p>", "created": "2015-03-17T03:39:53Z", "uid": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "anon": "no"}], "data": {"embed_links": []}, "bucket_name": "Today", "is_tag_endorse": false, "children": [], "tag_endorse": [], "tag_endorse_arr": [], "created": "2015-03-17T03:39:53Z", "id": "i7cr4pb46hp5hw", "type": "i_answer"}, {"no_upvotes": 0, "uid": "hs2ssz7dkh76h6", "bucket_name": "Last week", "bucket_order": 5, "updated": "2015-03-17T05:13:24Z", "config": {}, "anon": "no", "data": {"embed_links": null}, "folders": [], "subject": "<p>如果采用老的实现的话&#xff0c;所有trap都会被当成interrupt处理。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>trap和interrupt处理的不同之处在于interrupt gate会将IF flag清零而trap gate不会。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>也就是说&#xff0c;在老的实现下&#xff0c;操作系统在处理trap的时候将无法响应maskable interrupt&#xff0c;这会导致功能和标准出现不同。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>一个简单的例子就是&#xff0c;当我们的应用程序产生了一个trap的时候&#xff0c;我们本来可以通过键盘强制关闭该程序&#xff0c;但是此时键盘的中断信号无法被接收&#xff0c;必须等到trap处理完才能得到响应。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>即便如此&#xff0c;在大多数情况&#xff0c;操作系统仍然可以正常完成其功能&#xff0c;而且用户很难发现有何不同。</p>", "children": [{"uid": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "bucket_name": "Last week", "bucket_order": 5, "updated": "2015-03-17T16:15:56Z", "config": {}, "anon": "no", "data": {"embed_links": null}, "folders": [], "subject": "<p>Excellent!</p>", "children": [], "type": "feedback", "created": "2015-03-17T16:15:56Z", "id": "i7di503qsea5om"}], "type": "followup", "no_answer": 0, "created": "2015-03-17T05:13:24Z", "id": "i7cugz304ur4vj"}, {"no_upvotes": 0, "uid": "i78odcf1aiM", "bucket_name": "Yesterday", "bucket_order": 3, "updated": "2015-03-21T14:46:00Z", "config": {}, "d-bucket": "Yesterday", "data": {"embed_links": null}, "anon": "no", "folders": [], "subject": "32号可能有NMI  全部是trap还是有点不妥", "children": [{"uid": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "bucket_name": "Today", "bucket_order": 2, "updated": "2015-03-22T03:09:31Z", "config": {}, "anon": "no", "data": {"embed_links": null}, "folders": [], "subject": "<p>如果是NMI错误&#xff0c;系统应该是彻底不行了&#xff0c;OS已经无能为力了。</p>", "children": [], "type": "feedback", "created": "2015-03-22T03:09:31Z", "id": "i7jv8wolle227"}], "type": "followup", "no_answer": 0, "created": "2015-03-21T14:46:00Z", "id": "i7j4oqnoucd1sz"}], "request_instructor": 0, "tags": ["lab1", "student"], "s_edits": [], "num_favorites": 1}, "aid": "iajgy60gul86m2"}